3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with learning a transformation to translate input images into a specified domain, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with multiple modalities of input images, which is a subfield of multimedia. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with generating images, which is a subfield of computer graphics.
